data.revised_prompt: Create a photorealistic, professional-quality image of a 'Cranberry Bourbon Blush' cocktail served in a classic rocks glass. The cocktail should exhibit a deep, vibrant ruby color, illuminated subtly by warm light that brings forward the amber undertones of the bourbon. Three fresh cranberries float on the surface, providing a contrast against the drink. The rim of the glass is coated with sugar sparkles reflecting the light. The setting is a rustic wooden table with a soft, blurred backdrop of autumn leaves and bokeh lights to instill a warm, cozy, and elegant ambiance. Please ensure the visual composition complements the mood of the cooler seasons. There should be no text or watermarks, only a clear background with a soft focus to enhance the photorealistic style.
